name: gone to the dogs
description:
"gone to the dogs" is the 3rd song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. Sampling an old muppets record the beat is hard and dusty, perfect to snap your neck to. 

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "gone to the dogs"  

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality WAV files!
